所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • SQLite,
  • SQLite.JDBC2x

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • SQLite.Backup
    • SQLite.Benchmark
      • SQLite.BenchmarkDataSource
      • SQLite.BenchmarkDriver
    • SQLite.Blob
    • SQLite.Constants
    • SQLite.Database
    • SQLite.FunctionContext
    • SQLite.JDBC
      • SQLite.JDBCDataSource (implements javax.sql.DataSource)
      • SQLite.JDBCDriver (implements java.sql.Driver)
    • SQLite.JDBC2x.JDBCConnection (implements SQLite.BusyHandler, java.sql.Connection)
    • SQLite.JDBC2x.JDBCDatabaseMetaData (implements java.sql.DatabaseMetaData)
    • SQLite.JDBC2x.JDBCResultSet (implements java.sql.ResultSet)
    • SQLite.JDBC2x.JDBCResultSetMetaData (implements java.sql.ResultSetMetaData)
    • SQLite.JDBC2x.JDBCStatement (implements java.sql.Statement)
      • SQLite.JDBC2x.JDBCPreparedStatement (implements java.sql.PreparedStatement)
    • SQLite.Shell (implements SQLite.Callback)
    • SQLite.SmokeTest
    • SQLite.SQLDump (implements SQLite.Callback)
    • SQLite.SQLiteJDBCLoader
    • SQLite.SqliteJniTest
    • SQLite.SQLRestore
    • SQLite.Stmt
    • SQLite.StringEncoder
    • SQLite.TableResult (implements SQLite.Callback)
      • SQLite.JDBC2x.TableResultX
    • java.lang.Throwable (implements java.io.Serializable)
      • java.lang.Exception
        • SQLite.Exception
    • SQLite.Vm

接口分层结构
